notice.venue: Shaheed Bhagat Singh College, University of Delhi
notice.title: Youth Conclave 2023
notice.text: Youth Conclave 2023 is the first edition of two-day long Model United Nations Conference at Shaheed Bhagat Singh College, University of Delhi. Youth Conclave will be conducted on 22-23 April, 2023 at college premises. In these two days, the delegates shall debate, deliberate and discuss upon some most pressing issues of the world.
